Top NewsNational Center for Theoretical Science (NCTS) will be 20 years old this year August. In the past 20 years, NCTS has made significant contribution in shaping the research of theoretical physics and building up of the community in Taiwan.  It has also served as an effective network the home researchers with scholars and preeminent institutions abroad. A number of activities will be organized throughout the year to celebrate the anniversary. In particular there will be a 20th anniversary celebration meeting of NCTS on August 2-3, 2017 at NCTS, National Tsing-Hua University. We cordially invite you to participate and help to make it a memorable event.
